About
We don't collect or store any of your personal information. If you choose to use iCloud with Wikipanion then your bookmarks and history can be stored on Apple's iCloud servers but they remain inaccessible to us. We occasionally gather completely anonymized statistics on average user session length and how frequently average users use the app, all of which are supplied by Apple in accordance with their privacy policy.
Wikimedia (the people that run Wikipedia) may collect and store some information about what you access on their servers. Please see the
Wikimedia privacy policy for details.
Using Wikipanion you can access third party wikis. Please see their respective web sites for their own privacy policies which apply when accessing their third party servers.